 to the mountains, escaping persecution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSoon the best property of a Muslim will be a flock of sheep he takes to the top of a mountain, or in the valleys of rainfall, fleeing with his religion from tribulations.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":617,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/11\/signs-hour-sin-fitnah-murder\/","url_meta":{"origin":6116,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Killing, upheaval, sin before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Time will pass rapidly, knowledge will be withdrawn, tribulations will prevail, greed will be cast into hearts, and there will be many upheavals.\u201d They said, \"What is upheaval?\" The Prophet said, \"It is killing.\" Source: \u1e62a\u1e25\u012b\u1e25 al-Bukh\u0101r\u012b 7061,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37083,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/05\/refuge-fitnah-dajjal\/","url_meta":{"origin":6116,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Seek refuge from tribulations, torment of grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, this nation will be put to trial in their graves. Were it not that you would stop burying each other, I would have called upon Allah to make you hear the punishment of the grave as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6113,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/fitnah-ummah-punished-trials\/","url_meta":{"origin":6116,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: This Ummah punished in the world with trials","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThis nation of mine has been granted mercy. Their punishment is not in the Hereafter. Their punishment is in the world through persecution, earthquakes, and slaughter.\" Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4278 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2943,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/18\/people-wish-death-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":6116,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Trials: People wish for death before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established un